<tt xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml" xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" xmlns:tts="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#styling" xmlns:amll="http://www.example.com/ns/amll" xmlns:itunes="http://music.apple.com/lyric-ttml-internal" itunes:timing="Word"><head><metadata><ttm:agent type="person" xml:id="v1"/><ttm:agent type="other" xml:id="v2"/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="Innocence"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="塞壬唱片-MSR"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="ユリカリパブリック"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="松林凜"/><amll:meta key="album" value="Innocence"/><amll:meta key="ncmMusicId" value="3375918502"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithub" value="113187535"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithubLogin" value="marenol1mg"/></metadata></head><body dur="03:27.701"><div begin="00:23.089" end="03:27.701"><p begin="00:23.089" end="00:27.264" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L1"><span begin="00:23.089" end="00:23.369">How</span> <span begin="00:23.369" end="00:24.027">many</span> <span begin="00:24.027" end="00:25.049">winter</span><span begin="00:25.049" end="00:25.385">s</span> <span begin="00:25.752" end="00:25.940">in</span> <span begin="00:25.940" end="00:26.099">a</span> <span begin="00:26.099" end="00:27.264">gaze</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">一次凝望，望穿了多少冬天</span></p><p begin="00:27.768" end="00:30.113" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L2"><span begin="00:27.768" end="00:27.984">Lost</span> <span begin="00:27.984" end="00:28.112">in</span> <span begin="00:28.112" end="00:28.413">side</span> <span begin="00:28.413" end="00:28.744">a</span> <span begin="00:28.744" end="00:30.113">maze?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">迷途中失去方向</span></p><p begin="00:30.891" end="00:35.324" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L3"><span begin="00:30.891" end="00:31.072">And</span> <span begin="00:31.072" end="00:31.329">how</span> <span begin="00:31.329" end="00:32.057">many</span> <span begin="00:32.057" end="00:32.877">feeling</span><span begin="00:32.877" end="00:33.003">s</span> <span begin="00:33.729" end="00:34.005">un</span><span begin="00:34.005" end="00:35.324">spoken,</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">有多少思绪不曾言说</span></p><p begin="00:35.734" end="00:38.086" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L4"><span begin="00:35.734" end="00:36.082">Held</span> <span begin="00:36.082" end="00:36.394">in</span> <span begin="00:36.394" end="00:36.712">this</span> <span begin="00:36.712" end="00:38.086">hand?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">尽数敛于手掌</span></p><p begin="00:38.892" end="00:43.332" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L5"><span begin="00:38.892" end="00:39.072">The</span> <span begin="00:39.072" end="00:39.345">weight</span> <span begin="00:39.345" end="00:40.014">of</span> <span begin="00:40.014" end="00:40.117">the</span> <span begin="00:40.117" end="00:40.392">old</span> <span begin="00:40.392" end="00:41.438">skies</span> <span begin="00:41.738" end="00:41.912">on</span> <span begin="00:41.912" end="00:42.077">my</span> <span begin="00:42.077" end="00:43.067">shoulder</span><span begin="00:43.067" end="00:43.332">s</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">旧日的重量压在肩头</span></p><p begin="00:43.772" end="00:45.698" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L6"><span begin="00:43.772" end="00:44.066">Sun</span> <span begin="00:44.066" end="00:44.385">light</span> <span begin="00:44.385" end="00:44.704">in</span> <span begin="00:44.704" end="00:45.698">disguise</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">伪装成阳光模样</span></p><p begin="00:45.733" end="00:47.018" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L7"><span begin="00:45.733" end="00:46.048">Who</span> <span begin="00:46.048" end="00:46.618">would</span> <span begin="00:46.618" end="00:46.743">have</span> <span begin="00:46.743" end="00:47.018">known</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">又有谁能预料</span></p><p begin="00:47.373" end="00:53.343" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L8"><span begin="00:47.373" end="00:47.673">There's</span> <span begin="00:47.673" end="00:48.033">an</span> <span begin="00:48.033" end="00:49.063">end</span> <span begin="00:49.063" end="00:49.423">to</span> <span begin="00:49.423" end="00:53.343">eternity?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">永恒也有其终章</span></p><p begin="00:53.689" end="00:56.898" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L9"><span begin="00:53.689" end="00:54.032">The</span> <span begin="00:54.032" end="00:55.003">lone</span> <span begin="00:55.003" end="00:55.383">tale</span> <span begin="00:55.383" end="00:55.831">is</span> <span begin="00:55.831" end="00:55.989">no</span> <span begin="00:55.989" end="00:56.898">more</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">独行往事至此落幕</span></p><p begin="00:57.123" end="01:00.730" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L10"><span begin="00:57.123" end="00:57.388">As</span> <span begin="00:57.388" end="00:57.718">a</span> <span begin="00:57.718" end="00:58.353">breeze</span> <span begin="00:58.353" end="00:58.652">brush</span><span begin="00:58.652" end="00:59.031">es</span> <span begin="00:59.031" end="01:00.730">by</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">当微风一阵阵拂过</span></p><p begin="01:01.073" end="01:04.709" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L11"><span begin="01:01.073" end="01:01.343">As</span> <span begin="01:01.343" end="01:01.693">the</span> <span begin="01:01.693" end="01:02.032">days</span> <span begin="01:02.032" end="01:02.598">drift</span> <span begin="01:02.598" end="01:03.043">on</span> <span begin="01:03.043" end="01:04.709">by</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">当日子一天天流过</span></p><p begin="01:05.074" end="01:09.029" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L12"><span begin="01:05.074" end="01:05.389">Found</span> <span begin="01:05.389" end="01:05.509">a</span> <span begin="01:05.509" end="01:06.564">steady</span> <span begin="01:06.564" end="01:07.749">shore</span> <span begin="01:07.699" end="01:08.019">of</span> <span begin="01:08.019" end="01:09.029">trust</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我在广袤的大地上</span></p><p begin="01:09.100" end="01:11.849" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L13"><span begin="01:09.100" end="01:09.409">In</span> <span begin="01:09.409" end="01:09.684">this</span> <span begin="01:09.684" end="01:10.389">vast</span> <span begin="01:10.389" end="01:11.849">world</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">找到了值得信赖的坚实湾港</span></p><p begin="01:13.074" end="01:16.682" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L14"><span begin="01:13.074" end="01:13.389">As</span> <span begin="01:13.389" end="01:13.682">we</span> <span begin="01:13.682" end="01:14.034">walk</span> <span begin="01:14.034" end="01:14.600">side</span> <span begin="01:14.600" end="01:15.004">by</span> <span begin="01:15.004" end="01:16.682">side</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN"> 当我们并肩同行</span></p><p begin="01:17.024" end="01:20.709" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L15"><span begin="01:17.024" end="01:17.334">The</span> <span begin="01:17.334" end="01:17.694">script</span> <span begin="01:17.694" end="01:18.009">is</span> <span begin="01:18.009" end="01:18.584">fad</span><span begin="01:18.584" end="01:19.034">ing</span> <span begin="01:19.034" end="01:20.709">away</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">命运瓦解冰消</span></p><p begin="01:21.048" end="01:24.858" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L16"><span begin="01:21.048" end="01:21.373">And</span> <span begin="01:21.373" end="01:21.683">the</span> <span begin="01:21.683" end="01:22.633">frozen</span> <span begin="01:22.633" end="01:23.693">dawn</span> <span begin="01:23.693" end="01:23.858">stream</span><span begin="01:23.858" end="01:24.063">s</span> <span begin="01:24.063" end="01:24.858">forth</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">曾冻结的曙光融作溪流潺潺向前</span></p><p begin="01:25.069" end="01:29.015" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L17"><span begin="01:25.069" end="01:26.445">Into</span> <span begin="01:26.445" end="01:26.725">the</span> <span begin="01:26.725" end="01:29.015">new</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">流入新的一方</span></p><p begin="01:48.002" end="01:50.153" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L18"><span begin="01:48.002" end="01:48.345">Now</span> <span begin="01:48.345" end="01:48.860">I</span> <span begin="01:48.860" end="01:49.012">can</span> <span begin="01:49.012" end="01:50.153">see</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">如我所见</span></p><p begin="01:51.064" end="01:54.848" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L19"><span begin="01:51.064" end="01:51.361">You</span> <span begin="01:51.361" end="01:51.659">were</span> <span begin="01:51.659" end="01:51.995">alway</span><span begin="01:51.995" end="01:52.272">s</span> <span begin="01:52.272" end="01:52.847">there</span> <span begin="01:52.847" end="01:53.031">for</span> <span begin="01:53.031" end="01:54.848">me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你们一直在我身旁</span></p><p begin="01:55.062" end="01:57.010" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L20"><span begin="01:55.062" end="01:55.740">Set</span><span begin="01:55.740" end="01:55.903">ting</span> <span begin="01:55.903" end="01:56.072">my</span> <span begin="01:56.072" end="01:56.356">burd</span><span begin="01:56.356" end="01:56.513">en</span> <span begin="01:56.513" end="01:57.010">down</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">卸下身上重担</span></p><p begin="01:57.589" end="01:59.011" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L21"><span begin="01:57.589" end="01:57.729">A</span> <span begin="01:57.729" end="01:57.890">quiet</span> <span begin="01:57.890" end="01:58.072">spr</span><span begin="01:58.072" end="01:58.385">ing</span> <span begin="01:58.385" end="01:58.534">has</span> <span begin="01:58.534" end="01:59.011">come</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">静谧的春天已经来到</span></p><p begin="01:59.787" end="02:04.270" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L22"><span begin="01:59.787" end="02:00.073">I</span> <span begin="02:00.073" end="02:01.777">am</span> <span begin="02:01.777" end="02:01.929">in</span> <span begin="02:01.929" end="02:02.077">a</span> <span begin="02:02.077" end="02:03.055">brand</span> <span begin="02:03.055" end="02:04.270">new</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我把旧事翻去，翻开</span></p><p begin="02:05.087" end="02:06.099" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L23"><span begin="02:05.087" end="02:06.099">chapter</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">崭新篇章</span></p><p begin="02:28.086" end="02:31.696" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L24"><span begin="02:28.086" end="02:28.376">As</span> <span begin="02:28.376" end="02:28.746">a</span> <span begin="02:28.746" end="02:29.101">breeze</span> <span begin="02:29.101" end="02:29.541">brush</span><span begin="02:29.541" end="02:30.011">es</span> <span begin="02:30.011" end="02:31.696">by</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">当微风一阵阵拂过</span></p><p begin="02:32.072" end="02:35.712" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L25"><span begin="02:32.072" end="02:32.430">As</span> <span begin="02:32.430" end="02:32.755">the</span> <span begin="02:32.755" end="02:33.057">days</span> <span begin="02:33.057" end="02:33.559">drift</span> <span begin="02:33.559" end="02:34.016">on</span> <span begin="02:34.016" end="02:35.712">by</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">当日子一天天流过</span></p><p begin="02:36.044" end="02:40.079" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L26"><span begin="02:36.044" end="02:36.415">Found</span> <span begin="02:36.415" end="02:36.719">a</span> <span begin="02:36.719" end="02:37.539">steady</span> <span begin="02:37.539" end="02:38.394">shore</span> <span begin="02:38.732" end="02:39.030">of</span> <span begin="02:39.030" end="02:40.079">trust</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我在广袤的大地上</span></p><p begin="02:40.079" end="02:42.652" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L27"><span begin="02:40.079" end="02:40.403">In</span> <span begin="02:40.403" end="02:40.697">this</span> <span begin="02:40.697" end="02:41.403">vast</span> <span begin="02:41.403" end="02:42.652">world</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">找到了值得信赖的坚实湾港</span></p><p begin="02:44.033" end="02:47.483" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L28"><span begin="02:44.033" end="02:44.395">As</span> <span begin="02:44.395" end="02:44.715">we</span> <span begin="02:44.715" end="02:45.043">walk</span> <span begin="02:45.043" end="02:45.557">side</span> <span begin="02:45.557" end="02:45.994">by</span> <span begin="02:45.994" end="02:47.483">side</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">当我们并肩前行</span></p><p begin="02:48.057" end="02:51.677" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L29"><span begin="02:48.057" end="02:48.362">The</span> <span begin="02:48.362" end="02:48.697">script</span> <span begin="02:48.697" end="02:49.017">is</span> <span begin="02:49.017" end="02:49.575">fad</span><span begin="02:49.575" end="02:50.012">ing</span> <span begin="02:50.012" end="02:51.677">away</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">命运瓦解冰消</span></p><p begin="02:52.056" end="02:55.926" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L30"><span begin="02:52.056" end="02:52.371">And</span> <span begin="02:52.371" end="02:52.671">the</span> <span begin="02:52.671" end="02:53.566">frozen</span> <span begin="02:53.566" end="02:54.116">dawn</span> <span begin="02:54.636" end="02:54.916">stream</span><span begin="02:54.916" end="02:55.116">s</span> <span begin="02:55.116" end="02:55.926">forth</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">曾冻结的曙光融作溪流潺潺向前</span></p><p begin="02:55.979" end="02:59.648" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L31"><span begin="02:55.979" end="02:56.328">The</span> <span begin="02:56.328" end="02:56.645">weight</span> <span begin="02:56.645" end="02:56.965">of</span> <span begin="02:56.965" end="02:58.026">yester</span><span begin="02:58.026" end="02:59.648">day</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">昨日的重负</span></p><p begin="03:00.016" end="03:03.708" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L32"><span begin="03:00.016" end="03:00.348">Will</span> <span begin="03:00.348" end="03:01.017">never</span> <span begin="03:01.017" end="03:01.524">hold</span> <span begin="03:01.524" end="03:02.008">me</span> <span begin="03:02.008" end="03:03.708">again</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">今日不再能束缚我身</span></p><p begin="03:04.068" end="03:07.715" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L33"><span begin="03:04.068" end="03:04.388">Cause</span> <span begin="03:04.388" end="03:04.722">when</span> <span begin="03:04.722" end="03:05.020">the</span> <span begin="03:05.020" end="03:05.476">tide</span><span begin="03:05.476" end="03:05.573">s</span> <span begin="03:05.573" end="03:06.420">turn</span> <span begin="03:06.700" end="03:07.030">and</span> <span begin="03:07.030" end="03:07.715">sway</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">即便世事潮汐起落无常</span></p><p begin="03:08.087" end="03:10.642" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L34"><span begin="03:08.087" end="03:08.477">We'll</span> <span begin="03:08.477" end="03:08.727">know</span> <span begin="03:08.727" end="03:09.402">our</span> <span begin="03:09.402" end="03:10.642">way</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我们知道要去往何方</span></p><p begin="03:12.017" end="03:15.622" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L35"><span begin="03:12.017" end="03:12.342">Don't</span> <span begin="03:12.342" end="03:12.677">need</span> <span begin="03:12.677" end="03:13.012">to</span> <span begin="03:13.012" end="03:13.737">be</span> <span begin="03:13.737" end="03:15.622">afraid</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">无需惧怕</span></p><p begin="03:16.037" end="03:19.687" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L36"><span begin="03:16.037" end="03:16.312">Set</span> <span begin="03:16.312" end="03:16.687">sail</span> <span begin="03:16.687" end="03:17.017">and</span> <span begin="03:17.017" end="03:17.562">row</span> <span begin="03:17.562" end="03:19.687">away</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">扬帆起航</span></p><p begin="03:20.042" end="03:22.347" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L37"><span begin="03:20.042" end="03:20.692">Never</span> <span begin="03:20.692" end="03:21.017">felt</span> <span begin="03:21.017" end="03:21.522">so</span> <span begin="03:21.522" end="03:22.347">safe</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">从未如此安心</span></p><p begin="03:22.716" end="03:27.701" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L38"><span begin="03:22.716" end="03:23.039">With</span> <span begin="03:23.039" end="03:23.584">you,</span> <span begin="03:23.584" end="03:24.054">I</span> <span begin="03:24.054" end="03:24.349">can</span> <span begin="03:24.349" end="03:24.684">step</span> <span begin="03:24.684" end="03:25.496">into</span> <span begin="03:25.496" end="03:25.621">the</span> <span begin="03:25.621" end="03:27.701">new</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">有你们相伴，我能奔赴新的篇章</span></p></div></body></tt>